HEADWORD: Dilacerate
<hw>Di*lac"er*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Dilacerated</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Dilacerating</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>dilaceratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>dilacerare</ets> to tear apart;
